{"tid":860553,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我的女僕殿下","createTime":"2018-10-13T12:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T12:29:06.000Z","uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43f30b1b58daa747449940f241d80466680d3628","tid":860553,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"封底<br />\n<br />\n身爲皇室的遺一合法繼承者&mdash;卡瑟琳，一點都不想成為女皇。<br />\n<br />\n為了人民的安危和幸福，她喪權辱國，向他俯首稱臣。<br />\n<br />\n「這樣不是很有趣嗎？卡瑟琳陛下。你因為保護人民而出賣尊嚴，人民卻唾棄你。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n「嗯....嗯....」卡瑟琳像狗一樣跪在地上，舔藉他的腳指，只可以含糊應他。"},{"pid":"a582ec3c09fec207cbab2b49b82d4e22be09cdbb","tid":860553,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}